channel.title: Strange notice
channel.description: I was just doing my first install of the most recent version of whonix. I shut down the gateway and before it would shut off, it asked me if I wanted to close out a TTY "login" or "session" or something. Should this be cause for alarm?

item.title: Strange notice
item.dc:creator: Patrick
item.description:
No alarm. (The tty session is rads https://www.whonix.org/wiki/Desktop#RAM_Adjusted_Desktop_Starter.)

Read full topic
